        <updateDate>2019-10-09T21:44:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Sunshine Protection Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill makes daylight savings time the new, permanent standard time.</p> <p>States with areas exempt from daylight savings time may choose the standard time for those areas.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
